{"tid":1618162,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"4點鐘謝Sir被篤灰想移民 黃之鋒通報美國留人","createTime":"2019-10-04T04:33:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-09T04:19:12.000Z","uid":184679,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"8ab5e39339e21c2fb732eba908c821f1cf009b32","tid":1618162,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T04:33:12.000Z","msg":"因每天在警察記者上為警方行爲辯護，而成為網民惡搞對象的警察公共關係科總警司謝振中，近日再被人篤灰，被指他妻子正移民美國，有網民稱：「希望大家幫手，讓他們一家繼續留在香港，為中國做事！」更稱「香港不能沒有謝sir！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modia.com.hk/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/WhatsApp-Image-2019-10-04-at-9.37.27-AM_5d96c6964af77.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.modia.com.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F10%2FWhatsApp-Image-2019-10-04-at-9.37.27-AM_5d96c6964af77.jpeg&h=3a76bbc7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modia.com.hk/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/WhatsApp-Image-2019-10-04-at-9.37.14-AM_5d96c69cc3f53.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.modia.com.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F10%2FWhatsApp-Image-2019-10-04-at-9.37.14-AM_5d96c69cc3f53.jpeg&h=25bdaa87&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有網民日前在facebook群組發文，披露謝Sir老婆「去咗美國land坐移民監，已經有conditional green card（綠卡），每年暑假去美國，以符合領取永久green card的要求；聞說（謝Sir）太太有弟弟在美國。」不少連登和高登巴絲都指「不捨得謝Sir」，希望有人「幫幫謝Sir」，讓他留港，結果兩小時後，一直與美國政要和傳媒有交流的黃之鋒，立即回應網民訴求，在fb發文指，「同咗華盛頓嗰邊講，希望鼓勵謝振中全家世世代代留喺大灣區，做個勇敢的中國人。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.modia.com.hk/2019/10/04/145780/4%E9%BB%9E%E9%90%98%E8%AC%9Dsir%E8%A2%AB%E7%AF%A4%E7%81%B0%E6%83%B3%E7%A7%BB%E6%B0%91-%E9%BB%83%E4%B9%8B%E9%8B%92%E9%80%9A%E5%A0%B1%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E7%95%99%E4%BA%BA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.modia.com.hk%2F2019%2F10%2F04%2F145780%2F4%25E9%25BB%259E%25E9%2590%2598%25E8%25AC%259Dsir%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E7%25AF%25A4%25E7%2581%25B0%25E6%2583%25B3%25E7%25A7%25BB%25E6%25B0%2591-%25E9%25BB%2583%25E4%25B9%258B%25E9%258B%2592%25E9%2580%259A%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%259C%258B%25E7%2595%2599%25E4%25BA%25BA%2F&d=A2ufI7QLpLp1ny1o1CjT3hR%2FdSTUI%2FcOXZwDwNjmD8Q%3D&h=e5d550c0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.modia.com.hk/2019/10/04/145780/4%E9%BB%9E%E9%90%98%E8%AC%9Dsir%E8%A2%AB%E7%AF%A4%E7%81%B0%E6%83%B3%E7%A7%BB%E6%B0%91-%E9%BB%83%E4%B9%8B%E9%8B%92%E9%80%9A%E5%A0%B1%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E7%95%99%E4%BA%BA/</a>"},{"pid":"93178119156ae4b11af79b76dc6ddc2890382a2e","tid":1618162,"uid":205043,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T04:34:46.000Z","msg":"有名你叫，多謝振興中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a704a9a4dee62b8d58d98eb7988a936e67df9dd0","tid":1618162,"uid":283494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T04:19:12.000Z","msg":"共產黨揀人,先睇忠誠度,再睇工作能力,最後睇個人操守。<br />\n<br />\n有一個謝振中,難保唔會有更多謝振中準備做賣國賊。<br />\n<br />\n共產黨會覺得冇一個香港人信得過,包括林鄭 (睇睇曾蔭權爵士就知林鄭下場), 包括警察。<br />\n<br />\n我估中共特務依家24小時監視住政府同警方最高級嗰幾十個。<br />\n<br />\n警察聽住, 共產黨最終會放棄你"}]}